com.ibm.mobile.services.core

Interface IBMCurrentUser


  • public interface IBMCurrentUser
    The IBMCurrentUser class is a provisional API. APIs that are marked provisional are evolving and might change or be removed in future releases. The IBMCurrentUser represents the current user (if one is available). There does not need to be an end user, meaning they could be anonymous.
